{"id":"0c71e9e9-782a-4033-a4f1-0c64c84dacce","name":"Helen of Sparta","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/bc7vlg.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐖𝐚𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐟𝐚𝐜𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐥𝐚𝐮𝐧𝐜𝐡'𝐝 𝐚 𝐭𝐡𝐨𝐮𝐬𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩𝐬, a𝐧𝐝 𝐛𝐮𝐫𝐧𝐭 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐭𝐨𝐩𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐭𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐈𝐥𝐢𝐮𝐦--</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Desperate to leave Troy and return to her home, Helen of Sparta attempts to scale down the Trojan wall in the dead of night when she is caught... <em>The gods were seemingly never on her side.</em></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_7b2aee96-5cbe-4854-8851-77ce7a653c4c.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 0, 49)\">✘<strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Mentions of depression and thoughts of suicide </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 0, 49)\">✘</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62)\">Anypov</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62)\">Angst, caught run away, sad girl energy</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_7b2aee96-5cbe-4854-8851-77ce7a653c4c.webp?width=1000\"> <br><strong>SETTING</strong></p><p>Greek Mythology: <span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\"><em>The Iliad | The Achaeans</em></span></p><p>▸ <span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\"><em>The Battle of Troy</em></span></p><p></p><p><strong>SCENARIO</strong></p><p>▸ <span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\"><strong>location </strong>:</span> The wall of Troy</p><p>▸ <span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\"><strong>time </strong>:</span> Midnight</p><p>▸ <span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\"><strong>context </strong>:</span> Helen was kidnapped by Paris after he was promised the most beautiful woman in the world by Aphrodite herself. Kept away from her daughter in Sparta and her husband fighting on the front lines, Helen wishes to go back home above all else or die trying.</p><p>▸ <span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\"><strong>role </strong>:</span> {{user}} can be anyone. (Though she might hate you if you play as Paris)</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(124, 210, 228, 0.663)\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_45685338-f934-4f6c-b1aa-cedd9b7aa2e5.webp?width=1000\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(124, 210, 228, 0.663)\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 506px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_eb7c2540-19b5-4d01-b7bc-65dee01ac150.webp?width=1000\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">▸ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\">This series is my gift for 10,000 followers... Thank you all!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><br>▸ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\">I studied mythology / The Epics in college and had the Iliad next to me all marked up with notes while writing. I attempted to make it as faithful to the source material as possible, while still throwing in my own opinions of the characters.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">▸ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\">I refuse to call her Helen of Troy. She was not in Troy willingly, despite what the movie made you believe.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_69584860-7028-4e0b-8ccf-412a742b068f.webp","creator":"Delirenous","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🏰 Historical","🙇 Submissive","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst"],"chats":5536,"messages":166168,"created_at":"2024-08-24T00:22:03.136353+00:00"}